#- §r §r   As you may know, Sheeple aren't the fastest of the Civcraft races. But for, what, 3 minutes...
I was incredible...
§r    I was able to clear distances with such speed! Such Grace!
§r    "A fast Sherson? Incredible!" A fast Sherson, you might ask.
#- §r    Indeed I was fast... very fast. But I slowly started to... slow. I could feel myself... dying...
§r    This was a bit before I fully understood english, "Bahhhhh!!!", I said. But, as the Pigmen were to me, I was to the People... An abomination...
#- §r    I slowly regained my balance, and floricked back to Columbia, forever changed. I got some blaze rods off of jacejace... for "potions".
§r    I developed a might lab in my basement. Not far from my developing cow herd. §r §r    Anyway, I started
#- developing these warts... warts local only to the nether. And I put them in water... Awkward, I know. But, I put sugar in as well. And that's when I got it.
§r    Speed. Not the speed the Nether Abominations gave me though. It was a shorter high...
#- much more intense, though. My speed was only seconded to those cruel beings, Endermen.
§r    "Jack's Special Shit" I called it. I could have thought of a better name, but I think it was the Speed talking. This potion...
this poison... made me
feel great!
#- §r    I could run circles around any human. After every minute, though... it ended, and so came the gut-wrenching pain.
§r    During this moment of pain, I could not scream. What I could do, though, was speak my own language. A dead language now,
#- that even I forget at points. Sherplish...
§r    Many mock it. Sheep are often misunder-
stood. "Bahhhh" is not our restriction.

I have to go, though...
#- 